text: Yana Dineva (; born 8 November 2002) is a Bulgarian footballer who plays as a defender for the Bulgaria women's national team. ==International career== Dineva capped for Bulgaria at senior level in a 0–6 friendly loss to Croatia on 14 June 2019. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Bulgarian women's footballers Category:Bulgaria women's international footballers
